# OGC Maps Core

Use these rules for all non-trivial changes:

- Read `.claude/skills/project-conventions/SKILL.md` before coding.
- Keep `packages/map-ui-lib` framework-agnostic (no MapLibre imports).
- Build fully controlled UI components for domain data.
- Use `mapui:` Tailwind prefix inside `packages/map-ui-lib`.
- Follow data flow: Config -> Zod -> Zustand -> App -> URL (nuqs).

Use the matching skill for focused tasks:

- Add component: `.claude/skills/add-map-component/SKILL.md`
- Add OGC hook: `.claude/skills/add-ogc-hook/SKILL.md`
- Extend config schema: `.claude/skills/extend-map-config/SKILL.md`
- Load GIS data: `.claude/skills/load-gis-data/SKILL.md`
- Troubleshoot OGC API: `.claude/skills/ogc-api-troubleshoot/SKILL.md`

Development workflow reference:

- `.agent/workflows/development.md`
